	* gtk/gtkiconview.c (gtk_icon_view_set_cursor): Document that
	@cell must be one of the renderers of the icon view, warn if 
	it is not, and ignore @start_editing if @cell is not set.
	(#335001, Emmanuel Rodriguez)

