	* gtk/gtkfilechooserdefault.c
	(gtk_file_chooser_default_class_init): Make GDK_KP_Divide pop up
	the location dialog populated to "/".
	(tree_view_keybinding_cb): Likewise.
	(trap_activate_cb): Likewise.

