	Fix #316871, reported by Dan Winship:
	
	* gdk/gdkwindow.h (struct _GdkWindowObject): Add a shaped flag.

	* gdk/x11/gdkwindow-x11.c (gdk_window_shape_combine_mask) 
	(gdk_window_shape_combine_region): Set it here.

