	Fix for #314004, reported by Michael Reinsch:

	* gdk/gdk.symbols:
	* gdk/gdkscreen.[ch]: Add gdk_screen_get/set_font_options_libgtk_only()
	Add gdk_screen_get/set_resolution_libgtk_only()

